div.p:
“Since you equate complete maturation with accomplishing the four 
                        factors,Five other Mahāyāna sūtras 
                            (Toh 248; 
                        Toh 249; 
                            Toh 250; 
                            Toh 251; 
                            and Toh 252) discuss “Accomplishing the four factors”
                        (chos bzhi sgrub pa or bzhi pa sgrub
                                pa) but the presentation here is not consistent across these texts, nor are any of
                        them consistent with the four factors presented here. what is your acceptance
                        based on?” Śāriputra asked.
